high_descs: Turn left and walk to the rectangular table in the dining room.
Pick up the ladle from the table.
Walk past the table and forward then right into the sink.
Wash the ladle in the bathroom sink.
Leave the bathroom turn left and walk to the rectangular diningtable.
Set the ladle down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Wash the ladle and put it on the diningtable

high_descs: Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the ladle from the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the ladle into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the diningtable.
Put the ladle on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Washed and placed the ladle on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the dining table on your right.
Pick up ladle from the desk.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the bed.
anns.task_desc: washing ladle on the sink and placing it clean.
